OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finvestigation unit after   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fclaims                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, McDonald's has launched a new          
OL,6, investigation handling unit after the  
OL,7, BBC reported on dozens of abuse        
OL,8, allegations at the fast-food chain.    
OL,10,FAlistair Macrow, chief executive of    
OL,11,FMcDonald's UK and Ireland, said the    
OL,12,Fclaims he had heard this week are      
OL,13,F"personally and professionally         
OL,14,Fshocking".                             
OL,16,FHe apologised to anyone affected.      
OL,18,FA BBC investigation was told workers,  
OL,19,Fsome as young as 17, are being groped  
OL,20,Fand harassed almost routinely.         
